How to build
------------

This package provides an interface for the www.agner.org/random Randomc library.


CREDITS/LICENSES
-----------------

The Randomc is licensed under the GNU GPL v3, as is this R package.
The Randomc sources in this R package have been copied from the randomc.zip package,
available here: http://www.agner.org/random/randomc.zip
Then the files randomc.h, sfmt.h were extracted and copied in the inst/include directory
and sfmt.cpp extracted and copied to the src/ directory.

